symbols.description:
Component that can be used as a wrapper component for custom pages.<br/>The component can be used in case you want to use SAP Fiori elements Building Blocks or XML template
constructions. You can either extend the component and set the viewName and contextPath within your code
or you can use it to wrap your custom XML view directly the manifest when you define your custom page
under sapui5/routing/targets:<br/><pre>
"myCustomPage": {
"type": "Component",
"id": "myCustomPage",
"name": "sap.fe.core.fpm",
"title": "My Custom Page",
"options": {
	"settings": {
		"viewName": "myNamespace.myView",
		"contextPath": "/MyEntitySet"
		}
	}
}
</pre>
